M

Main - Class in game
This is the main class that is used to run the whole game and has the functionality of the zombies, bullets, player and etc.
Main() - Constructor for class game.Main
The default constructor for the main game.
main(String[]) - Static method in class menu.Menu
When the game starts the game opens with the menu first.
mapSetup() - Method in class game.Main
The method for map setup where it sets the borders that zombies and players cannot go through.
menu - package menu
 
Menu - Class in menu
This is the class for the menu where when the game starts it displays the menu rather than playing the game right away, it also includes multiple options to access the instructions, scoreboard, and backstory classes.
Menu() - Constructor for class menu.Menu
The default constructor for the Menu.

The method for where it controls the actual movement for the zombies (speed).
